---
import SectionTitle from './SectionTitle.astro';
import FocusIcon from './FocusIcon.astro';
---

<section class="py-16">
  <SectionTitle
    eyebrow="About"
    title="把工程能力和审美表达结合起来"
    description="智能车辆工程背景，在学 Web 全栈和自动驾驶。"
  />

  <div class="grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
    <div data-reveal class="group glass-card rounded-[1.75rem] p-6 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_26px_72px_rgba(6,78,59,0.13)]">
      <FocusIcon kind="code" />
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-bold text-emerald-950">工程开发</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        独立做了 LeafVault：FastAPI 写后端、SQLite 管数据、PWA 前端、Docker 部署。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div data-reveal class="group glass-card rounded-[1.75rem] p-6 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_26px_72px_rgba(6,78,59,0.13)]">
      <FocusIcon kind="vehicle" />
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-bold text-emerald-950">智能车辆</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        智能车辆工程专业在读，参与 Apollo 自动驾驶比赛，学习路径规划和仿真技术。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div data-reveal class="group glass-card rounded-[1.75rem] p-6 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_26px_72px_rgba(6,78,59,0.13)]">
      <FocusIcon kind="visual" />
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-bold text-emerald-950">视觉创作</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        学过 Blender、Lightroom、摄影构图和光影，对画面和配色比较敏感。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div data-reveal class="group glass-card rounded-[1.75rem] p-6 transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1.5 hover:shadow-[0_26px_72px_rgba(6,78,59,0.13)]">
      <FocusIcon kind="language" />
      <h3 class="mt-4 font-bold text-emerald-950">English Fluency</h3>
      <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-600">
        Passed CET-6, keep building vocabulary every day, and aim to read technical documentation fluently with strong spoken English.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
